column1:
The Gitcoin Sybil Slaying Hackathon was concerned more about the novelty of the idea,
the significance of the features discovered and the clarity of the approaches (with 
the help of good visualizations). To avoid possible confusion and misunderstandings, 
we choose to hide the output lists of suspicious Sybils formally presented in the folder 
(It is not a main point of the Hackathon). But, if you are full of curiousity about the output
of your personal address, follow trustalabs on Twitter for a query :-)

Gitcoin比赛评判侧重于思路新颖性，特征显著性和方法清晰度（包括结果的可视化展示）。
为了减少误解，我们选择隐藏本目录下之前输出的地址列表（争论这些结果是否是真的女巫并不是比赛的重点）。
但是，如果您非常关注自己的个人地址在本次算法输出的结果，请在Twitter上关注Trustalabs，并私信查询。
"
